{"tid":1537370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"以後入場睇港隊比賽請不要噓義勇軍進行曲","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:21:36.000Z","uid":53000,"like":77,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"df02a7ad4d8bfda47a896492adf9b9decf3274d1","tid":1537370,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"試下學呢間學校嘅學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中學早會播國歌 學生唱do you hear the people sing 抗議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後入場睇港隊比賽請不要噓義勇軍進行曲，<br />\n奏樂時站立，肅然起敬<br />\n全場大合唱 問誰未發聲<br />\n入場前如果派到歌紙就派<br />\n派唔到就算"},{"pid":"5e74bbf065e0d9fda14fb9106f153c88f4b4d1dc","tid":1537370,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccb1b59bfabc6b90fbe84c7f115746df0ff2bd39","tid":1537370,"uid":59134,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"唱美國國歌"},{"pid":"accd164de4bff953a7e8088625d5d11bcdd52bbe","tid":1537370,"uid":69472,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:02:35.000Z","msg":"我係保棠人呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db00e1f36f8c838c44c6ef1191793b227187c59a","tid":1537370,"uid":60658,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩 傳統嚟"},{"pid":"e0219137d1de19ae52bc0c5aeba93f66da5eaf6e","tid":1537370,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be09d334aa4410b0b4c2da698524d96728640811","tid":1537370,"uid":60658,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"e0219137d1de19ae52bc0c5aeba93f66da5eaf6e","tid":1537370,"uid":21275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db00e1f36f8c838c44c6ef1191793b227187c59a","tid":1537370,"uid":60658,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩 傳統嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:08:03.000Z","msg":"噓匪歌係港隊比賽傳統"},{"pid":"2b26855f6ccab43826f68dbafdbe5d7ca48f541d","tid":1537370,"uid":86277,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"唱do you hear the people sing文宣效果勁好多<br />\n一係問吓球員聽邊樣士氣激昂啲"},{"pid":"a50c7d2bd2c32b4e3aa92784bdfc216083ecb5bd","tid":1537370,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019